glis held posts in ford lio hotaiwan and ford europeessex england mr inglis earned his ba in business economics with honors from strathclyde university in glasgow scotland he currently serves on the boards of directors for brookhaven science associates llc utbattelle llc and carpenter technology corporation a leading manufacturer and distributor of specialist alloys and engineered products he is a member of the conference board council of cfos transactions date shares transaction value     disposition at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share      disposition at  per share      derivativenonderivative trans at  per share  copyright  factset research systems inc all rights reserved source factset fundamentals officers and executives mr tony r thene president chief executive officer  director mr joseph e haniford chief operating officer  senior vice president mr damon j audia chief financial officer  senior vice president mr james a johnson chief information officer  vice president mr brian j malloy chief commercial officer  vice president mr timothy lain chief accounting officer vp  controller mr william j rudolph headmedia relations mr john l rice vice presidenthuman resources mr james d dee secretary vice president  general counsel mr steven e karol independent director dr jeffrey wadsworth independent director ms kathryn c turner independent director mr peter n stephans independent director mr i martin inglis independent director mr stephen maurice ward independent director mr robert r mcmaster independent director dr philip m anderson independent director mr carl g anderson independent director log in  pm edt july   marketstatecountryus new york closed marketstatecountryuk london closed marketstatecountryjp tokyo open marketstatecountryus   marketstatecountryuk   marketstatecountryjp   view all latest news newslatest p totally avoidable reasons why millennials can’t have nice things or save any